{# Travel update card #}
<h2>Travel update card</h2>
{# What #}
<h3>What is it?</h3>
<ul>
    <li>A card with disruption indicator components in, which show the live status of a bus, train or tram route and roads.</li>
</ul>
{# When to #}
<h3>When to use it?</h3>
<ul>
    <li>When the live status of a mode of transport is useful to the content. For example, showing the live status of train lines next to content about trains.</li>
</ul>
{# When not to #}
<h3>When not to use it?</h3>
<ul>
    <li>When the live status is irrelevant to the content. Users can find this information on the homepage.</li>
</ul>

{# Set up travel updates #}
{% from "wmnds/patterns/content-cards/travel-updates/_travel-updates.njk" import wmndsContentCardTravelUpdates %}

{{
    compExample([
